b911 b911 d f1
b911 b911 u 01 01
b911 b911 s 	pop psw!
b912 b912 d a0
b912 b912 u 01 01
b912 b912 s  ana b ;low bits removed from A
b913 b913 d 91
b913 b913 u 01 01
b913 b913 s 	sub c!
b914 b914 d e61f
b914 b914 u 02 01
b914 b914 s  ani maxext ;set flags
b916 b916 d c1
b916 b916 u 01 01
b916 b916 s 	pop b ;restore original values
b917 b917 d c9
b917 b917 u 01 01
b917 b917 s 	ret
b918 b918 s ;
b918 b918 s search:
b918 b918 s 	;search for directory element of length C at info
b918 b918 d 3eff
b918 b918 u 02 01
b918 b918 s 	mvi a,0ffh!
b91a b91a d 32d4bf
b91a b91a u 03 01
b91a b91a s  sta dirloc ;changed if actually found
b91d b91d d 21d8bf
